<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/lucy-rigby> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Lucy Rigby MP was appointed as Chief Secretary to the Treasury on 14 May 2026. She was previously Parliamentary Secretary (Economic Secretary to the Treasury) at HM Treasury from 6 September 2025 to 14 May 2026 and Solicitor General between 2 December 2024 and 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Northampton North in July 2024."@en .
